===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A two-wheeled motorized vehicle with a step-thru frame
# A motorized chair with three or four wheels that steers using handlebars designed for people with limited mobility
# A vehicle consisting of a long [[platform]] mounted on two wheels, the front one of which has an [[upright]] [[handle]] for [[steering]], propelled by a small motor
# [[child]]'s [[foot]]-[[operated]] [[vehicle]] consisting of a long [[platform]] mounted on two wheels, the front one of which has an [[upright]] [[handle]] for [[steering]], propelled by resting one foot on the footboard and pushing the other against the ground
# A [[sailing]] [[vessel]] with a flat bottom and [[runner]]s for travelling over [[water]], [[ice]], or [[snow]]
# A motorboat resembling a motor scooter
# An item of diving equipment used by scuba divers to increase their range while underwater
# An ultralight helicopter of co-axial rotor configuration
# A fictional vehicle used by the character Darth Maul in the movie Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace
# A large, black [[duck]]; the [[scoter]].
# ''colloquial''A Harley Davidson motorcycle


